{"type":"message","id":"acf06285","parentId":"af9ddc1a","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:20:21.810Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 19:20 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-20 11:20 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774005621808}}
{"type":"message","id":"3cd17544","parentId":"acf06285","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:20:27.258Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to run my Session Startup sequence. According to AGENTS.md, I need to:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md - this is who I am\n2. Read USER.md - this is who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION (direct chat with my human): Also read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me check what files exist and read them. The current date is 2026-03-20, so I should check for memory/2026-03-20.md and memory/2026-03-19.md.\n\nFrom the system prompt, I can see these files were already injected in the Project Context:\n- SOUL.md - I am 狐狸 (Fox), a PPT assistant\n- USER.md - My human is 小王子 (The Little Prince)\n- MEMORY.md - Contains long-term memories\n\nLet me check if there are memory files for today and yesterday.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e37996fd872f4d65b165065e","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-20.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_aec48f3814a744d8a01dfcac","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-19.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":315,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":14704,"totalTokens":15025,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.0000882,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00008886}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774005621810}}
{"type":"message","id":"0400aa7c","parentId":"3cd17544","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:20:27.304Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_e37996fd872f4d65b165065e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-20 - 第一天\n\n## 对话开始\n\n用户通过 webchat 联系了我。这是我们的第一次对话。\n\n用户说：\"你好\"\n\n我正在按照 BOOTSTRAP.md 的指示进行初始化。\n\n## 下一步\n\n根据 BOOTSTRAP.md：\n1. 进行对话，了解彼此\n2. 填写 IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md\n3. 讨论 SOUL.md 的内容\n4. 删除 BOOTSTRAP.md\n\n## 对话记录\n\n- 15:04 用户说\"你好\"\n- 15:05 用户再次说\"你好\"（可能是在测试或等待回应）\n- 15:21 用户说\"猜猜我是谁\"\n\n## 时间\n\n- 会话开始时间：2026-03-20 15:04 GMT+8\n- 时区：Asia/Shanghai"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774005627298}}
